  "description": "<p>在今天举办的微软全球合作伙伴（WPC 2013）大会上，Windows 8.1再度成为主角之一。微软表示，Windows 8.1从开发之初的理念就是让这款系统更加人性化。 Windows部门老大Tami Reller在开场演讲中说<strong>，Windows 8.1是为了让人们感觉更加自然更加舒服，在这一理念的基础上，开发团队对Windows 8.1进行了诸多改进，例如恢复了开始按钮。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e63ddc2/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244002.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9AWindows+8.1%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E8%AE%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%9B%B4%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244002.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9AWindows+8.1%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E8%AE%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%9B%B4%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244002.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9AWindows+8.1%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E8%AE%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%9B%B4%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244002.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9AWindows+8.1%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E8%AE%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%9B%B4%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244002.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9AWindows